Package: SeuratSourcery
Type: Package
Title: A data harmonization package for scRNA-seq data integration projects
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Joseph", "Duraisingh",
      email = "josephduraisingh@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
      comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0000-9548-9256")
    )
  )
Description: SeuratSourcery is a comprehensive all in one tool that allows for
    various single cell transcriptomic datasets to be merged into a single 
    differential expression analysis cleanly. Accepted file types so far include
    .rds, .h5ad, .loom, .csv and 10x reads. Intended for downstream analysis 
    in Seurat.
